fragment_downloaded_cb({"url": "Comparisons.html#page-description", "fragment": "Comparing Meson with other build systems \nA common question is Why should I choose Meson over a different build system X There is no one true answer to this as it depends on the use case. Almost all build systems have all the functionality needed to build medium to large projects so the decision is usually made on other points. Here we list some pros and cons of various build systems to help you do the decision yourself. \n"});